#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-more-SMP-transforms.md:1
msgid "Add SMP support to more transform classes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release_details/9.4/add-more-SMP-transforms.md:3
msgid ""
"SMP acceleration has been implemented for nearly all of the VTK transform "
"classes (that is, classes derived from vtkAbstractTransform).  Previously "
"only vtkTransform and similar vtkLinearTransform-derived classes were "
"accelerated. Implemented now: vtkIdentityTransform, vtkGridTransform, "
"vtkBSplineTransform, vtkThinPlateSplineTransform, vtkPerspectiveTransform, "
"vtkCylindricalTransform, and vtkSphericalTransform."
msgstr ""
